'''Andriyya dil Virroccio''' neɣ s tutlayt Tatalyanit : '''Andrea del Verrocchio''' (attayen n. 1435 – 1488) ikka-t-nn iga yan "sculptor" [[Talyan|aṭalyani]], adhaybi d umekla. Tekka-tt-nn dar-s yat tsawert ilan azal ɣ ammas n Flurinsa, kkan-t-nn gan kigan d imeklawen n tleslalit; inelmaden d yimeswurrin-nnes. Zun d [[Botticini]], [[Domenico Ghirlandaio|Ghirlandaio]] d [[Pietro Perugino|Perugino]], macc anlmad nns akkʷ ittyawssanen [[Leonardo Da Vinci|Leonardo da Vinci]] ad t-igan. 
